hierarchy: LOCAL
type: reserved
description: "Local-only groups"
groups: local.*
comment: [
    "Historically reserved for local groups and occasionally configured"
    "for such groups in news software.  It is not really a good idea for"
    "sites to use this hierarchy for local groups, since they may occur"
    "on many unconnected sites and may confuse news readers that read at"
    "multiple sites."
]
